actions.message:
**!help**                                              - Displays this menu
**!customenchants** (!ce)              - Displays a menu for the custom enchants
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
Reply with the starting number to display the custom enchants for that group.

**1** - Global enchants
**2** - Tools
**3** - Armor
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Water breathing** - Gives you water breathing while equipped
**Speed** - Gives you speed while equipped
**Levitation** - Gives you levitation while eqipped
**Gust** - Sends you in the direction youre looking at when right clicked
**Haste** - Gives you haste while equipped
**Luck** - When you break a block, anything from coal to diamonds can be dropped
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Experience** - Gives you experience when you break a block (*Pickaxe only*)
**Vacuum** - Any drops from blocks are automatically added to your inventory (*Pickaxe only*)
**Explosion** - Triggers an explosion when you break a block (*Pickaxe only*)
**Auto Smelt** - Automatically smelts what you mine (*Pickaxe and shovel only*)
**Gold Rush** - Has a chance to drop a gold nugget when you break sand (*Shovel only*)
**Chopper** - Breaks the entire tree when you break part of it (*Axe only*)
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
**Nether Step** - Allows you to walk on lava when sneaking (*Boots only*)
**Angelic Step** - Allows you to walk on air when sneaking (*Boots only*)
**Feather Falling** - Blocks all fall damage (*Boots only*)
**Green Thumb** - Grows whatever you're standing (*Leggings only*)
